pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: header-badge
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 24, 160, 20]
    content:
      style: "$badge"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: FIXINTEL PRO

  - elementId: page-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 60, 1000, 45]
    content:
      style: "$title"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>Фитнес-клубы теряют деньги на <span style="color:$accent;">рутине</span></p>

  - elementId: title-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 110, 50, 3]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: card1-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 140, 373, 180]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$border"

  - elementId: card1-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [80, 158, 32, 32]
    iconName: "fas:file-excel"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: card1-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [122, 156, 290, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: Ручной учёт клиентов

  - elementId: card1-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 198, 333, 105]
    content:
      style: "$bodySmall"
      fontSize: 15
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Ошибки в базе, потерянные контакты, дубли. Клиенты "исчезают" после покупки абонемента.</p>

  - elementId: card2-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [453, 140, 374, 180]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$border"

  - elementId: card2-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [473, 158, 32, 32]
    iconName: "fas:door-open"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: card2-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [515, 156, 290, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "Нет контроля доступа"

  - elementId: card2-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [473, 198, 334, 105]
    content:
      style: "$bodySmall"
      fontSize: 15
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>"Проходят знакомые", протёкшие абонементы. Невозможно отследить кто реально посещает.</p>

  - elementId: card3-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [847, 140, 373, 180]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$border"

  - elementId: card3-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [867, 158, 32, 32]
    iconName: "fas:money-bill-wave"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: card3-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [909, 156, 290, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: Кассовые разрывы

  - elementId: card3-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [867, 198, 333, 105]
    content:
      style: "$bodySmall"
      fontSize: 15
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Нет прозрачности выручки. Ручные Z-отчёты, ошибки в налоговой, штрафы от ФНС.</p>

  - elementId: card4-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 340, 373, 180]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$border"

  - elementId: card4-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [80, 358, 32, 32]
    iconName: "fas:chart-line"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: card4-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [122, 356, 290, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: Аналитика в голове

  - elementId: card4-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 398, 333, 105]
    content:
      style: "$bodySmall"
      fontSize: 15
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Не понимают, когда пик, кто уходит, какая зона приносит деньги. Решения на догадках.</p>

  - elementId: card5-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [453, 340, 374, 180]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$border"

  - elementId: card5-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [473, 358, 32, 32]
    iconName: "fas:user-tie"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: card5-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [515, 356, 290, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: Тренеры в Excel

  - elementId: card5-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [473, 398, 334, 30]
    content:
      style: "$bodySmall"
      fontSize: 15
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Расписание на листочке, клиенты в телефоне. Нет системы учёта тренировок.</p>

  - elementId: card6-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [847, 340, 373, 180]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$border"

  - elementId: card6-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [867, 358, 32, 32]
    iconName: "fas:clock"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: card6-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [909, 356, 290, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: Админ на рутине

  - elementId: card6-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [867, 398, 333, 105]
    content:
      style: "$bodySmall"
      fontSize: 15
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>40% времени — на заполнение журналов, поиск карточек, ручную отчётность вместо продаж.</p>

  - elementId: bottom-stat
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 550, 1160, 70]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 20
      color: "$accent"
      align: [center, middle]
      text: |
        <p><strong>В среднем клуб теряет 15-25% выручки из-за отсутствия автоматизации</strong></p>

  - elementId: bottom-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 690, 40, 3]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: page-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1180, 688, 40, 20]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "02"